  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个工业IoT系统的闭环控制流程图。核心是从TelemetryStream采集数据，经过MQTT Broker，最后驱动PLC Logic。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream",
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker",
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，TelemetryStream作为起点，先到MQTT Broker，再到PLC Logic。PLC之后是直连执行器吗？还是有多个控制层级？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic",
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "PLC后面需要串联多个ActuatorController，形成级联控制。我数了一下，大概需要六个ActuatorController节点，从D到I编号。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，六个ActuatorController串联：D→E→F→G→H→I。那I之后怎么闭环？需要回到MQTT Broker还是直接回TelemetryStream？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController",
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker",
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "I之后先回到MQTT Broker，再由Broker把控制反馈传回TelemetryStream，形成完整的闭环。这样系统能持续监听执行结果。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker",
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已经画好了：A(TelemetryStream)→B(Broker)→C(PLC)→D→E→F→G→H→I(ActuatorController)→B→A。您看看结构对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream",
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker",
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic",
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，B到C的箭头方向我确认一下——PLC Logic应该接收Broker的指令，这个方向是对的。但I到B的箭头需要再确认，反馈数据应该是上行到Broker。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker",
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic",
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认I→B是上行反馈，B→A是闭环回到TelemetryStream。目前所有箭头都是单向顺时针，符合数据流向。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController",
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker",
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "六个ActuatorController的命名需要区分吗？还是统一用ActuatorController？实际场景中D到I可能是不同工位的控制器。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "建议保持统一命名为ActuatorController，用节点ID D到I区分。如果后续需要细化，可以再添加工位标签。这样图面更简洁。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "同意，统一命名更清晰。另外确认一下闭环：A→B→C→D→E→F→G→H→I→B→A，这个循环没有遗漏节点吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream",
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker",
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic",
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "核对完成：起点A，经过B、C，进入六级联D-E-F-G-H-I，然后I返回B，B再回A。总共11个节点，10条有向边，闭环完整。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream",
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker",
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic",
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "B出现了两次，既是A的出口也是I的入口，这样设计会不会让人误解为两个不同的Broker？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "这是同一个MQTT Broker节点，只是作为中间枢纽被多次引用。在流程图中用同一标签B表示物理上同一个Broker，逻辑上是合理的。需要我标注说明吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 15,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "不用额外标注，工业场景下Broker作为数据总线被多次访问是常见设计。保持现状即可。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 16,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "最终确认：A[TelemetryStream]单向流向B[MQTT Broker]，再到C[PLC Logic]，然后串联D、E、F、G、H、I六个ActuatorController，I返回B，B再闭环回A。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream",
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker",
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic",
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 17,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "正确。这个闭环体现了完整的工业控制回路：采集→传输→决策→多级执行→反馈→再采集。可以定稿了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream",
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker",
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic",
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 18,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "最后确认节点标签格式：方括号内保持IoT_Industrial_前缀，如IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController，符合工业命名规范。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream",
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker",
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic",
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 19,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "前缀保留，这是企业命名规范。D到I虽然都是ActuatorController，但各自独立节点，不要合并。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 20,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已最终定稿。流程图呈现为TD（自上而下）布局，清晰展示从TelemetryStream出发，经Broker和PLC，通过六级ActuatorController级联，最终闭环回到起点的完整工业IoT控制链路。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream",
